0.text: Lokuvela enkantolo futsi kusho lilanga lekucala lalommangalelwa kuba nelilungelo lekutsetsa licala ngekuphutfuma.

1.text: Lamuhla ekuseni, umoya bewuhhusha nga-83 wemakhilomitha ngeli-awa futsi bekulindzeleke kutsi uchubeke wehla.

2.text: Sitfo lesimcoka kakhulu seluhlelo lwekutungeleta yinhlitiyo, lefutsa ingati.

3.text: Lewebhusayithi bantfu labanyenti bayinakile, ikakhulukati labo labafundzako.

4.text: Kuvakasha kuyashipha uma nibaningi, ngako-ke nangabe uwedvwa noma unemngani munye, zama kutfola labanye bantfu nente licembu lalabane kuya kulabasitfupha litoba ncono linani lelibhadalwa ngumuntfu amunye.

5.text: Letinye tinhlelo temakhamera letimafilimu tisebentisa luhlelo lwe-6 x 6, lokukhulu nakakhulu ku-56 x 56 wemamilimitha.

6.text: Yenta bese uphatsa emakhopi enchubomgomo netinombolo temshuwalensi tibe kuwe.

7.text: Ekhaya kakho akunatfwe likhofi lelimnandzi ekuseni bese kunatfwa litiya ebusuku.

8.text: Lichwa leliwako tintfo letivamile, tindzawo letehlelako tiba nalo nje kodvwa leliningi lehlela entasi.

9.text: Umtselo ubalwa ngetindlela letingafani emaveni lahlukene, linani lemtselo liyehlukana kulelinye live nakuchatsaniswa nalelinye.
